   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Qualifications and Benefits </b>feature allows you to provide benefits at the bundle level for a set of products or categories. Bundles are a set of products grouped together and sold at a parent level, but not at the individual product level. For more information about Tiered and Non-tiered qualifications and benefits, refer to the <xref href="../qualifications_and_benefi_102432700/102432700.dita"
               format="dita"
               class="- topic/xref ">Qualifications and Benefits</xref> section.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <image placement="break"
                   width="700"
                   href="../attachments/102432712/107118620.jpg"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The following table describes the actions you can take on the Qualifications and Benefits page:</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Fields</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Bundle Name</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Select the bundle name for the set of products you want to buy.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product Name</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Add products or categories in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product Name</b> column. For adding products or categories, please refer to the <xref href="../adding-products_102432695_102432695/102432695.dita"
                                 format="dita"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">Adding Products</xref> section. Products are the list of products which are purchased by customers at the bundle level.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">UOM (Unit Of Measures)</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">It defaults to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Each</b>.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Type</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Auto-populated based on the products or categories selected.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Unit</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the unit of the product.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Unit Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the price of the product.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Extended Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Auto-calculated price for the whole unit of the product.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Bundle Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Aggregated price of the products that are grouped in the bundle.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
